headline: The Cigna Group Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: The Board of Directors of The Cigna Group (NYSE: CI) today declared a cash dividend of $1.51 per share of its common stock, payable on September 18, 2025 to shareholders of record as of the close of business on September 4, 2025.
